Sentencas: Ionic conductivity of perovskite oxides La0.8Sr0.2AlO2.9 with different size of B-site ions were measured.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of high purity Zn-doped (La0.8Sr0.2)AlO2.9 electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In addition, the behavior of lattice parameter with dopant content was investigated in terms of the size of the B-site ions and the tolerance factor of the perovskite structure: the ionic conductivity of La0.8Sr0.2Al1-xZnxO3-delta (LSAZ) was measured at various operating temperatures; from 500 to 800 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of high purity Zn-doped (La0.8Sr0.2)AlO2.9 electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Ionic conductivity was found to be significantly increased by adding small amount of Zn doping.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of high purity Zn-doped (La0.8Sr0.2)AlO2.9 electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The La0.8Sr0.2Al0.8Zn0.2O2.8 specimen showed ionic conductivities at 0.0304S cm(-1) at 800 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of high purity Zn-doped (La0.8Sr0.2)AlO2.9 electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The average thermal expansion coefficient (TEC) of La0.8Sr0.2Al0.8Zn0.2O2.8 was 10.07 x 10(-6)K(-1) in the temperature range from 40 to 800 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of high purity Zn-doped (La0.8Sr0.2)AlO2.9 electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: As a result, the La0.8Sr0.2Al0.8Zn0.2O2.8 is a prospective candidate as electrolyte material for solid oxide fuel cells in intermediate temperatures.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of high purity Zn-doped (La0.8Sr0.2)AlO2.9 electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
